      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STELLA SHADOWS (2) has a strong record this trip with four wins and three placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (35.19) when fourth over 600m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Looks a key chance on best form. ARCADIAN RUBY (1) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (35.27) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can improve sharply here. RED DAY (6) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including three wins. Below best last time at Sandown (30.17) in a Special conditions H, finishing a 6 length eighth. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. PARTY POPPER (7) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
